3. Hysteretic Model¶

3.1. Elastic¶

class ElasticType(TypedDict):
    type: Literal["elastic"]
    k0: float                       # 初期剛性[kN/m]

3.2. Bilinear¶

class BilinearType(TypedDict):
    type: Literal["bilinear"]
    k0: float                       # 初期剛性[kN/m]
    a1: float                       # 降伏後剛性低下率[-]
    f1: float                       # 降伏荷重[kN]

3.3. Trilinear, Gyakko, Takeda¶

class TrilinearType(TypedDict):
    type: Literal["gyakko", "takeda", "trilinear"]
    k0: float                       # 初期剛性[kN/m]
    a1: float                       # 降伏後剛性低下率1[-]
    a2: float                       # 降伏後剛性低下率2[-]
    f1: float                       # 降伏荷重1[kN]
    f2: float                       # 降伏荷重2[kN]
